{
  "texts": [
    "Sections 4 and 5 use historical VR literature and the most recent wave of XR research to discuss safety and privacy risks in IXR.",
    "Section 6 discusses how some extant EU legislation succeeds or fails in mitigating those threats.",
    "Section 7 outlines our recommendations to legislators; Section 8 concludes the article.",
    "This article aims to map the landscape of XR risks to inform policymakers, rather than comprehensively classifying or ranking the likelihood of all possible risks.",
    "To achieve this, we employ an iterative narrative literature review (Jahan et al., 2016)."
  ]
}